{"tid":1250531,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"麻煩做文宣嘅入嚟","createTime":"2019-06-22T06:09:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-23T02:54:55.000Z","uid":87598,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"90612de21e92dffa8e1d5c4635c0168af85b0dfc","tid":1250531,"uid":87598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T06:09:26.000Z","msg":"我覺得而家除咗要解釋惡法同埋重申訴求之外<br />\n我哋仲需要做一啲文宣以正視聽<br />\n呢幾日食飯特登行去聽啲阿叔講政治時事<br />\n好多上年紀嗰啲其實唔係唔支持爭取民主甚至香港獨立(題外話) <br />\n唔知點解講講下會去到呢個議題<br />\n但佢哋成日有一個前設 <br />\n就係而家香港嘅經濟同埋好多糧食或者飲用水都係靠中國提供 <br />\n假如香港冇咗中國就會仆街冚家剷 <br />\n所以佢哋寧願要佢哋阿爺提供穩定繁榮都唔要爭取民主 <br />\n我覺得除咗喺惡法呢件事上面要做文宣<br />\n要是沒有中國就仆街或者阿爺提供穩定經濟<br />\n香港比中國摙住春袋<br />\n呢幾方面都要做一啲文宣 以正視聽 如果唔係佢哋根本唔會同你傾<br />\n淨係覺得你哋繼續咁樣做係破壞香港經濟穩定繁榮<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當然我知道救義士同埋撤惡法係好迫切<br />\n但係你哋成日咁撚驚民意轉向<br />\n你哋應該要深入了解下點解佢哋會轉向或者唔支持你"},{"pid":"ca146d8e0f81f211bbb3fe75b7d9b4045c115c01","tid":1250531,"uid":87598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T06:24:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91a9a782bc0ed9925d0f0320a377113bc35f44c9","tid":1250531,"uid":87598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T06:30:08.000Z","msg":"你哋成日話要做文宣走入社區<br />\n不如你哋走入社區了解下香港人要啲乜嘢<br />\n再改進啲文宣"},{"pid":"a9678e80ef48b6ea62f19c92691e2e89f2f246a1","tid":1250531,"uid":87598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T06:34:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37dd3fbe5f8122e163d50fde81694272732a70d5","tid":1250531,"uid":152594,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T06:36:16.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n唔知點解好多人以為香港咩都要靠中國<br />\n明明係中國逼我地用/買中國野"},{"pid":"540732931b5d061975a0077d0a6e00f76b8620dd","tid":1250531,"uid":87598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"37dd3fbe5f8122e163d50fde81694272732a70d5","tid":1250531,"uid":152594,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T06:36:16.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n唔知點解好多人以為香港咩都要靠中國<br />\n明明係中國逼我地用/買中國野"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T06:47:17.000Z","msg":"感謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"109293f3252fc66922991a1639a41cce360e2245","tid":1250531,"uid":87598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T06:51:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45c91b8469094014ed31a1a526c2f6717c53bca1","tid":1250531,"uid":43081,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T06:56:28.000Z","msg":"全部真金白銀同上面買都當成係佢打救我地"},{"pid":"90f2fc6730ff84d0dc1e8bda4411b9845d5e539c","tid":1250531,"uid":87598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"45c91b8469094014ed31a1a526c2f6717c53bca1","tid":1250531,"uid":43081,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T06:56:28.000Z","msg":"全部真金白銀同上面買都當成係佢打救我地"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T06:58:39.000Z","msg":"佢哋真係唔知道㗎<br />\n所以先至要叫文宣幫手"},{"pid":"35e612287c77275e1c057684264f2f41e2e8f9ee","tid":1250531,"uid":53811,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T07:01:00.000Z","msg":"過咗G20開始可以打文宣戰<br />\n香港水電糧食問題，幾乎都係有alternative<br />\n<br />\n東江屎水，要不是香港比錢買，廣東d官哪兒來錢貪<br />\n<br />\n+ 海水化淡成本平咗好多<br />\n+ 逼兩電買大陸垃圾電<br />\n+ 糧食 本來已經食泰國澳洲米<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bc165d24d8f3f81fad8023b88d9b67307764be5","tid":1250531,"uid":87598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"35e612287c77275e1c057684264f2f41e2e8f9ee","tid":1250531,"uid":53811,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T07:01:00.000Z","msg":"過咗G20開始可以打文宣戰<br />\n香港水